OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7,CIs Tony Blair getting cold feetGover   
OL,8, his election commitment to legislation 
OL,9, for greater freedom to roam over open  
OL,10, country?                               
OL,12, TheCWhite PaperGthat ministers promised
OL,13, to publish by the end of 1997 giving   
OL,14, proposals to make the right to roam a  
OL,15, legal reality has still not appeared.  
OL,17,CWhat's happened to it?GThe Green Scene 
OL,18, endeavours to find out...              
