OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7,G"Last year, the campaign for freedom of
OL,8,Gthe hillsCseemed to be approaching     
OL,9,Cfruition,"Gsays Nicky Warden from The  
OL,10,GRamblers' Association.                 
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,G"For years Labour, in its manifesto,   
OL,13,Cpromised to legalise open roaming.     
OL,15,G"So when it was elected last summer and
OL,16,CEnvironment Minister Michael Meacher   
OL,17,Gsaid a White Paper would be published  
OL,18,Gbefore the New Year, ramblers were     
OL,19,Gover the moon!"                        
