OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7, "We're now well into the New Year and  
OL,8, as yet,Cno White PaperGon access to    
OL,9, open land has been published," says    
OL,10, rambler Nicky Warden.                  
OL,12, "The fear among access campaigners     
OL,13, like myself is that Downing Street has 
OL,14, become anxious about further angering  
OL,15,Cthe farming and land-owning lobby.     
OL,17, "Ministers have been shaken by the     
OL,18, scale ofCrural uprisingsGin defence of 
OL,19, fox hunting," she adds.                
