OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7,GEnvironment Minister, Michael Meacher  
OL,8,Gwas hoping to get anCaccess-to-the-    
OL,9,Ccountryside BillGinto the legislative  
OL,10,Gprogramme beginning next autumn, says  
OL,11,Grambler Nicky Warden.                  
OL,13,G"But unless his proposals are published
OL,14,Gsoon, the timetable will be impossibly 
OL,15,Gtight, indeedCthe Bill may never       
OL,16,Chappen.                                
OL,17,G                                       
OL,18,G"Promises were made ` now in power,    
OL,19,CLabour must fulfil them."              
