OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7,CThe Country Landowners' Association    
OL,8, believes there should be an increase in
OL,9, access to open land. A spokesman said: 
OL,11, "If access rights are granted,         
OL,12, thousands will have to be paid out to  
OL,13,Coffset a loss of land value.           
OL,15, "In addition, everyone's rights should 
OL,16, be considered ` not just walkers. The  
OL,17, Government has to think aboutCthe needs
OL,18,Cof everybodyG` including landowners and
OL,19, the environment."                      
