OL,5,CFREEDOM FOR RAMBLERS TO ROAM?          
OL,7,G"The Government has not got cold feet; 
OL,8,Git still intends to legislate for      
OL,9,Ggreater freedom to roam over open      
OL,10,Gcountry," says a spokesman from the    
OL,11,CDepartment Of The Environment.         
OL,12,G                                       
OL,13,G"The issue is a complex one ` one that 
OL,14,Cinvolves various Government departments
OL,15,Gand groups.                            
OL,17,C"Once all concerned have been informed 
OL,18,Gand given their replies, an            
OL,19,Gannouncement will be made."            
